 perfectly with the branding and d\u00e9cor of your event theme or product launch. As one agency ordered \u201csomething that goes well with the (hopefully) good weather and the South of France festival vibe\u201d. Never a problem for <strong>Red Radish<\/strong>! As well as these tasty bowl food ideas we will also be \u2018serving up\u2019 the best waiters, waitresses and glass and equipment hire. See you at this year\u2019s Lions Festival. It is going to be\u00a0 a busy one for sure!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Beef\u00a0 <strong>Bourguignon<\/strong> or Daube with caper and mustard mash<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Merguez sausage with couscous and harissa<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Cod, chorizo and saffron potato stew<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thai green chicken curry with jasmine rice<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Shepherds pie and minted peas<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Coq au Vin with parsley mash<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Pad Thai with tofu and peanut (v)<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Roasted\u00a0 Mediterranean and bean cassoluet (v)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Spicy sweet potato and green been curry with coriander rice(v)<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Bowl foods have for a while been all the rage in London and New York where they make a substantial and stylish alternative to canap\u00e9s. Now the chefs at established&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/catering-equipment-hire-french-riviera\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1918,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnot